---
import "@fontsource/fragment-mono";
import "../styles/global.scss";
import "../styles/sidebar.scss";
import { ViewTransitions } from 'astro:transitions';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="description" content="Links to corners of the web" />
    <title>Links</title>
    <ViewTransitions />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="sidebar-container">
      <span class="name">
        <a class="name-link" href="/">Yihui Hu</a>
      </span>
      <div style={{ maxWidth: "350px" }}>
        I reside in many corners of the web. I collect things on ✶✶ <a
          class="wavy-link"
          href="https://are.na/yihui-h"
          target="_blank">Are.na</a
        >. I always have my hands full with (side) projects, which I publish on
        💻 <a
          class="wavy-link"
          href="https://github.com/yihui-hu"
          target="_blank">GitHub</a
        > wherever possible. You can view a nice version of my resume on 📃 <a
          class="wavy-link"
          href="https://read.cv/yihui"
          target="_blank">Read.cv</a
        >, or find me on their new Twitter-lite, 🔖 <a
          class="wavy-link"
          href="https://posts.cv/yihui"
          target="_blank">Posts</a
        >. For the no-funny-business side of things, see my 💼 <a
          class="wavy-link"
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/yihuihu"
          target="_blank">LinkedIn</a
        >. I try to read as much as I can, and update my reading lists on 📚 <a
          class="wavy-link"
          href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/62844518-yihui"
          target="_blank">Goodreads</a
        > / <a
          class="wavy-link"
          href="https://oku.club/user/yihui"
          target="_blank">Oku</a
        >. I have an 📸 <a
          class="wavy-link"
          href="https://www.instagram.com/yihui_hu"
          target="_blank">Instagram</a
        >, but I'm not active on there. I'm not a big movie person but I've been
        watching more of them over the summer (2023), and was persuaded to make
        a 🍿 <a
          class="wavy-link"
          href="https://letterboxd.com/yihui"
          target="_blank">Letterboxd</a
        >, so I have that too. I also have ☁️ <a
          class="wavy-link"
          href="https://bsky.app/profile/yihui.bsky.social"
          target="_blank">Bluesky</a
        >. Though, most times, I'm on 🐦 <a
          class="wavy-link"
          href="https://twitter.com/_yihui"
          target="_blank">Twitter</a
        >. Phew.
      </div>
      <div style={{ paddingBottom: "55px" }}>
        <a href="/">← Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
